@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    tmp = (0.74 + v2)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.23)))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.63)
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.49 * tmp + 0.69) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.66)) - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.97) + (v1 + 0.86 / v2 + 0.82)))
    data[tid] = v0
